    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Deseed the<strong> sweet pointed pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
