    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>fresh tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>tagliatelle</strong> for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> tagliatelle</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
