    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has softened, add the <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until evaporated</p><p>Add the <strong>creamy stock</strong> and cook for 2-3 min further or until thickened</p><p>Once thickened, add the <strong>drained fresh tagliatelle</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy Cajun-style pepper with fresh tagliatelle</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the starchy pasta water if it's looking a little dry</p>",
